5 Section 2. Section 87-2-411, MCA, is amended to read:
6 "87-2-411. Migratory game bird, sandhill crane, and swan licenses -- fees -- disposition of
7 proceeds. (1) The fee for a resident to purchase the a migratory game bird license is $5.50 $10. The fee for a
8 nonresident to purchase the a migratory game bird license is $150.
9 (2) The fee for a resident to purchase a sandhill crane license is $10. The fee for a nonresident to
10 purchase a sandhill crane license is $75. A person who purchases a sandhill crane license must also purchase
11 a migratory game bird license.
12 (3) The fee for a resident to purchase a swan license is $10. The fee for a nonresident to purchase
13 a swan license is $75. A person who purchases a swan license must also purchase a migratory game bird
14 license.
15 (2)(4) Money received from the sale of migratory game bird, sandhill crane, and swan licenses must
16 be deposited in an account in the state special revenue fund for the use of the department and may be
17 expended only for the protection, conservation, and development of wetlands in Montana."
18
19 NEW SECTION. Section 3. Effective date. [This act] is effective March 1, 2026.
